{"title":"Alpitude Lays Up Superlight Carbon Stelvio HS GPS Mount For Lightest Integrated Cockpits","link":"https://bikerumor.com/alpitude-lays-up-superlight-carbon-stelvio-hs-gps-mount-for-lightest-integrated-cockpits/","date":1696528302000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-Roval-Alpinist-cockpit.jpg\" alt=\"Alpitude Stelvio HS ultralight carbon out-front GPS cycling computer mount for integrated bars, Roval Alpinist cockpit\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-Roval-Alpinist-cockpit.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-Roval-Alpinist-cockpit-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-Roval-Alpinist-cockpit-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-Roval-Alpinist-cockpit-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-Roval-Alpinist-cockpit-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-Roval-Alpinist-cockpit-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-Roval-Alpinist-cockpit-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Handmade in the Italian Dolomites since 2016, Alpitude’s Stelvio HS is probably the lightest and sleekest out-front computer mount for many of the most sought-after ultralight integrated road bike cockpits on the market. Offering a direct-mount solution for popular Deda, Roval, Specialized &amp; THM handlebars, the new full-carbon Stelvio HS also </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Alpitude Stelvio HS ultralight GPS mount for integrated bars</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_options.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_options.jpg\" alt=\"Alpitude Stelvio HS ultralight carbon out-front GPS cycling computer mount for integrated bars cockpits, options\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_options.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_options-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_options-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_options-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_options-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_options-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_options-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a><figcaption><em>all c. Alpitude</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Alpitude already lays claim to the ‘<a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/alpitude-stelvio-corretto-worlds-lightest-ultralight-carbon-out-front-gps-mount/\" target=\"_blank\">world’s lightest out-front computer mount</a>‘ with their recent Stelvio Corretto from just under 13g. But with more modern proprietary 1-piece ultralight bar+stem cockpits and integrated aerodynamic handlebars on the market, seemingly universal solutions like the Corretto just might not fit your fancy bar.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_Deda-Alanera.jpg\"><img width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_Deda-Alanera.jpg\" alt=\"Alpitude Stelvio HS ultralight carbon out-front GPS cycling computer mount for integrated bars, Deda Alanera cockpit\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_Deda-Alanera.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_Deda-Alanera-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_Deda-Alanera-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_Deda-Alanera-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_Deda-Alanera-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_Deda-Alanera-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_Deda-Alanera-400x225.jpg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_Deda-Alanera-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a><figcaption>on Deda Alanera cockpit</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>So, if you have one of these wildly light Roval <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/new-roval-alpinist-ultralight-bar-stem-seatpost-combo-terra-gravel-flex-post-more/\" target=\"_blank\">Alpinist</a> or extra aero Roval <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/all-new-roval-rapide-road-cockpit-one-piece/\" target=\"_blank\">Rapide</a> cockpits, or a Specialized Tarmac with its separate <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=sl7\" target=\"_blank\">SL7</a> stem you’re pretty limited to what computer mount you can use because of the unique mounting interface. The same goes for THM’s 78g full-carbon <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/thm-tibia-full-carbon-stem-trims-78-grams-fibula-brakes-switch-metal-carbon/\" target=\"_blank\">Tibia</a> stem, or Deda’s <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/eb17-deda-alanera-integrated-superleggera-bars-plus-disc-rim-brake-sl-carbon-wheels/\" target=\"_blank\">Alanera</a> integrated cockpit. All of these modern road cockpit setups feature unique shaping, and unfortunately also special faceplate accessory mounting interfaces.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Alpitude to the rescue!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech details</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-gravel.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-gravel.jpg\" alt=\"Alpitude Stelvio HS ultralight carbon out-front GPS cycling computer mount for integrated bars cockpits, from 19g\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-gravel.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-gravel-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-gravel-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-gravel-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-gravel-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-gravel-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>But Alpitude has a modular solution with their new full-carbon Stelvio HS computer mount that can adapt to all of these bars with a bit of varied hardware.  And they are still wicked light – just 19g for the Roval solutions vs. the stock 30g mount. Plus, the same patented carbon loop in the optional Combo kit adds less than 3g more, making it easily the lightest way to attach a GoPro or light.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_underside.jpg\"><img width=\"1500\" height=\"902\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_underside.jpg\" alt=\"Alpitude Stelvio HS ultralight carbon out-front GPS cycling computer mount for integrated bars cockpits, underside adjustability\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_underside.jpg 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_underside-297x179.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_underside-800x481.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_underside-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_underside-768x462.jpg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Alpitude makes all of their carbon mounts and custom alloy hardware in Italy. The Stelvio HS features 2-position device mounting that means it will fit large and small devices – like the Garmin <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/garmin-edge-540-and-840/\" target=\"_blank\">Edge 540/840</a> vs. the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/never-charge-your-gps-again-with-the-new-garmin-edge-1040-solar/\" target=\"_blank\">Edge 1040</a>. That means, buy one premium out-front mount now. And then it will still work even if you change cycling computers down the road. HS, btw stands for Hyper Short, as it is their shortest mount overall, even with big computer compatibility. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can of course also pick from different adapters to fit the most common cycling computer interface standards.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Alpitude Stelvio HS – Pricing, Options &amp; Availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_side-profile.jpg\"><img width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_side-profile.jpg\" alt=\"Alpitude Stelvio HS ultralight carbon out-front GPS cycling computer mount for integrated bars cockpits, side profile\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_side-profile.jpg 1600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_side-profile-297x167.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_side-profile-800x450.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_side-profile-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_side-profile-768x432.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_side-profile-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_side-profile-400x225.jpg 400w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_side-profile-1200x675.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new lightweight carbon Alpitude Stelvio HS GPS cycling computer mount is available for pre-order now. And delivery is slated from the end of this month. It sells for 105€ for the mount with unique hardware for your cockpit, and your choice of <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=garmin+edge\" target=\"_blank\">Garmin</a>, <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=polar\" target=\"_blank\">Polar</a>, or <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=wahoo+elemnt\" target=\"_blank\">Wahoo</a> interfaces. For 130€ you get the Combo kit, which also adds in the removable ultralight GoPro accessory mount. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-THM-Tibia-stem.jpg\"><img width=\"2260\" height=\"1356\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-THM-Tibia-stem.jpg\" alt=\"Alpitude Stelvio HS ultralight carbon out-front GPS cycling computer mount for integrated bars cockpits, THM Tibia stem\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-THM-Tibia-stem.jpg 2260w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-THM-Tibia-stem-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-THM-Tibia-stem-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-THM-Tibia-stem-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-THM-Tibia-stem-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-THM-Tibia-stem-1536x922.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Alpitude-Stelvio-HS-ultralight-carbon-out-front-GPS-cycling-computer-mount-for-integrated-bars_on-THM-Tibia-stem-2048x1229.jpg 2048w\" /></a><figcaption>on THM Tibia stem</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Pick from compatibility with Deda Alanera, Roval Alpinist, or Roval Rapide cockpits; or Specialized SL7 or THM Tibia stems. More cockpit compatibility is in the works for the new Stelvio HS.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://alpitude.cc/\" target=\"_blank\">Alpitude.cc</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/alpitude-lays-up-superlight-carbon-stelvio-hs-gps-mount-for-lightest-integrated-cockpits/\">Alpitude Lays Up Superlight Carbon Stelvio HS GPS Mount For Lightest Integrated Cockpits</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"f80d026537c538b4a33d68ffe2f6d4722b0008c1aa1e0ead9fbae7c84cb50ba7","category":"Cycling"}